S.FORM: aicu a ti aljenljeng lja tjaluvie mavan a kisansemenay a paiwan i taiwan, au timadju kemasi imaza i jinfeng a guan a 正興 a qinaljan. ka 2003 a caviljan, italadj ta kisansemenay a sengsengan kati Brandy a maciur a semenay, makalap ta kazalan pakatua tjaljananguaqan a namaciur a semenay a dantay itua 金曲獎. mekedri a kalakudain na kuba, avan nu sika puaming a semenay a sengsengan. ka 2012 a caviljan, timadju masan tua ruvelengedan a kamuku itua na kacalisian a tilibi. mata 2014 a caviljan, malang tua rikudu pinaka"東排三聲代", ka 2016 a caviljan malang tua na pinayuanan a semenay a rikudu pinaka "vavayan·女人", saka makalap ta kazalan pakatua tjaljananguaqan a kacalisian a rikudu itua 金曲獎. ka 2020 a caviljan, ti aljenljeng sikapudrusa malap ta kazalan tua tjaljananguaqan a kacalisian a rikudu itua 金曲獎 katua 2020 a caviljan a tjaljananguaqan a guhubi, saka tuata aza senay pinaka〈Thank You 感謝〉malap tua tjaljananguaqan a semenay itua 金曲獎.

aico a ti aljenljeng lja tjalovie mavan a kisansemenay a paiwan i taiwan, ao timadjo kemasi imaza i jinfeng a goan a 正興 a qinaljan. ka 2003 a caviljan, italadj ta kisansemenay a sengsengan kati Brandy a macior a semenay, makalap ta kazalan pakatoa tjaljanangoaqan a namacior a semenay a dantay itoa 金曲獎. mekedri a kalakodain na koba, avan no sika poaming a semenay a sengsengan. ka 2012 a caviljan, timadjo masan toa rovelengedan a kamoko itoa na kacalisian a tilibi. mata 2014 a caviljan, malang toa rikodo pinaka"東排三聲代", ka 2016 a caviljan malang toa na pinayoanan a semenay a rikodo pinaka "vavayan·女人", saka makalap ta kazalan pakatoa tjaljanangoaqan a kacalisian a rikodo itoa 金曲獎. ka 2020 a caviljan, ti aljenljeng sikapodrosa malap ta kazalan toa tjaljanangoaqan a kacalisian a rikodo itoa 金曲獎 katoa 2020 a caviljan a tjaljanangoaqan a gohobi, saka toata aza senay pinaka〈Thank Yoo 感謝〉malap toa tjaljanangoaqan a semenay itoa 金曲獎.
